window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Ryker is a Guardian bound by duty to protect his charge, Liza, and her daughter Renee, from the darkness that threatens to consume them. As they flee from Liza's abusive ex-husband, Ryker must confront not only the physical dangers that pursue them, but also the insidious forces of evil that lurk in the shadows. </p> <p>With his supernatural abilities and unwavering determination, Ryker will stop at nothing to keep them safe. But as the danger closes in, Liza begins to realize that there may be more to Ryker than meets the eye. Drawn to him in ways she can't explain, she finds herself torn between fear and desire. </p> <p>As the two of them navigate the treacherous path ahead, they will discover a love that transcends the boundaries of the ordinary world. But will it be enough to protect them from the darkness that threatens to consume them? </p> <p><i>Protector </i>is a gripping paranormal fantasy romance that will keep you on the edge of your seat until the very end. Prepare to be immersed in a world where love and danger collide, and where the line between human and demon is blurred.</p>"; 
